dbp:pretitle: Candidate for the U.S. Senate from Nebraska
Chairman and President, Pinnacle Bancorp, Inc.

text: John Sidney “Sid” Dinsdale (born 1952) was a Republican candidate for U.S. Senate in Nebraska. Dinsdale is president of Pinnacle Bancorp, Inc., with 130 banking locations in eight states and assets of $7.6 billion.
